instructions: put the dinner plate on the table cloth
Place the salad plate on top of the dinner plate.
Place the napkin on top of the salad plate.
Place the wine glass above the plates in top right corner.
Place the water glass to the right of the wine glass but down about and inch.
Place the salad fork to the left of the plates.
Place the dinner fork between the plates and the salad fork.
Place the knife on the right side of the plates.
Place the soup spoon to the right of the knife.
